headline: Human Trafficking Task Force searches Struthers home
author: Gerry Ricciutti
sentences: Investigators with the Human Trafficking Task Force, Struthers Police Department and the Mahoning County Sheriff’s Office were at a home on Sexton Street, near Hawthorne Street, on Thursday morning.
STRUTHERS, Ohio (WKBN) – Investigators searched a home in Struthers, looking for evidence of child pornography.
No arrests have been made yet, but devices were seized as part of the investigation.
